3.Method Third
Alter Command

Setps in Alter Command for Moving Databse to another Drive
 a) Set Database offline
    Alter Database DBNAME SET OFFLINE
 b) To Check Database location
    Select * from databasename.sys.database_files
    
  c) Alter Database DBNAme Modify File (Name = 'DBName, FileName ='E\Folder\DBNAME.mdf') GO  for mdf DD slly for LDF DB
  
  d ) Alter Database DBNAME SET online
